      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point. While it is currently drivable, the engine and suspension show signs of age, and you should expect some minor mechanical repairs in the near future. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and small dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear from regular use. It\u2019s a reliable enough choice for short commutes, but it lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model.",
