      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has undergone a comprehensive multi-point certification to ensure peak performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled pedigree and aesthetic perfection.",
