    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it's always sparkling clean. It runs like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' feel. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have the best time behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
