    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for your dream ride? You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s spent its life tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. Not a single scratch, dent, or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful fresh new-car smell. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so happy. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
