    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the subframe has been inspected and verified for structural integrity, while the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been addressed as proactive maintenance. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the sharp turn-in and neutral handling balance the E46 chassis is renowned for. With flawless paint depth and an immaculate undercarriage, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious driving enthusiast.",
